HEADWORD: Thrilling
<hw>Thrill"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Causing a thrill; causing
tremulous excitement; deeply moving; <as>as, a <ex>thrilling</ex>
romance</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Thrill"ing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Thrill"ing*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

